caption:
I’ve started watching My Hero Academia!! Well, I started a while ago and sort of… forgot to keep watching lol.

ANYWAY I wanted to try my hand at doodling Uraraka cuz she’s got one of the cutest designs for an anime character I’ve seen in a while. She’s round and sweet and I like her!!

These chibis are a fun style experiment! I’m going to be doing a few more here and there so keep an eye out~ 

Patrons of my $20 tier can get either one of these or a headshot commission monthly!!!

summary:
Hello beautiful people on Tumblr,  now I finally present to you my finished TodoMomo fanart.  Ｏ(≧▽≦)Ｏ
If you saw one of my...
body:
Hello beautiful people on Tumblr, now I finally present to you my finished TodoMomo fanart. Ｏ(≧▽≦)Ｏ

If you saw one of my latest posts, that means you’ve seen the messy sketch I firstly made. I worked really hard on this thing and it’s obviously different from the sketch.

Guys, after an epic battle that lasted 5 days, I’m proud to say that this fanart is something I made. It took me more time that I expected. The reason for that is that I actually sent my bestie screenshots of my progress, so she can tell me if something seems a bit off. I’ve redrawn this thing about 3 or 4 times. Sometimes I had this bad luck, when my app just stopped working and I had to redo what I did in the last hour. BTW, that happened a few times in those 5 days. Still, I’m glad with the final result and really happy for the big help my best friend gave me. It was hard even for her, cause she had to give me a constructive criticism and still not make me feel like trash for the mistakes I made. Todoroki seems a bit off, but no matter how much I tried, I never managed to fix him.(╥﹏╥)

Feel free to reblog this post, but don’t forget to give me some credit. I spent so much time on it, after all. And please don’t remove my cute, little, basic signature, if you’re going to post this outside Tumblr. Thank you a lot.

Also I’m close to 300 followers, so I think I’ll share with you how I actually look and some basic information. In other words - face reveal. I think that became a normal thing to do on the internet.

Have a wonderful day, you wonderful people and next time I’ll draw a RoyAi fanart, just so you know. ♪☆＼(^０^＼) ♪(／^-^)／☆
